_sText:
I was orginally making this for someone that wanted a scoutzknivez with low grav and no floor, i didnt notice the part mentioning v1.6 and not source :)
so i figured i'd do something else with it, theres now a dark underground area (you get nv at spawn so use it). depending on which door you leave by, you'll either get a scout or a shotty (hence the name).
you start off with low gravity, theres a switch on top to turn to it back to normal (it also makes the screen shades of gray).
